{"tid":2130054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷決定就被辭退　向大學校監提出上訴","createTime":"2020-07-29T04:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:28:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5b1a54c40ded3f41295e81ba417f0453ba0b11","tid":2130054,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540511-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540511-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6SUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=d74dfd8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540511-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0752e650\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540511-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港大校務委員會通過解僱法律系副教授戴耀廷。他今早在社交網站表示，決定向港大校監、即特首林鄭月娥，就校委會辭退他的決定提出上訴。戴耀廷說，雖然知道上訴不可能成功，但不會讓林鄭月娥在傷害香港學術自由的事上置身事外，大學以外勢力推翻大學的決定是昭然若揭，之後會否提出司法覆核，有待與律師團隊商量。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷表示，基於保密原則，他不能夠公開大學的文件，但與律師團隊商量後，他向大學提交的文件是可以公開的，公眾可從他提交的文件中，大概掌握爭議的地方是甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，雖然離開了港大的崗位，但不會停下法治的研究及教學工作，他計劃用一至兩年時間完成一本有關法治的普及讀物，亦會在香港社區推動法治教育，會為香港法治的重生而繼續抗爭，同時希望支援其他為香港法治重生而戰的人。"},{"pid":"acbf416dab30411ca40b87e12dd71c291fcccbef","tid":2130054,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"鄭月娥怎能置身事外呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88a588221275300863bf7c3a59fb495bf7ef8c7","tid":2130054,"uid":306914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"別讓淋奠跑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}